      "id": "PopularPost21866",
      "post_content": "This guy is not bad. Remember you can sacrifice as many artifacts as you like in response to each activation, making him a costly but effective sweeper in artifact heavy decks.\n  \n   \nEdit:\n  \n@OpenSeasonNoobs: May I direct you to rule 112.7a of the Comprehensive Rules:\n  \n   \n\"Once activated or triggered, an ability exists on the stack independently of its source. Destruction or removal of the source after that time won\u2019t affect the ability. ... if the source is no longer in the zone it\u2019s expected to be in at that time, its last known information is used. The source can still perform the action even though it no longer exists.\"",
      "posted_by": "holgir",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost21866\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">This guy is not bad. Remember you can sacrifice as many artifacts as you like in response to each activation, making him a costly but effective sweeper in artifact heavy decks.\r<br/> <br/>Edit:\r<br/>@OpenSeasonNoobs: May I direct you to rule 112.7a of the Comprehensive Rules:\r<br/> <br/>\"Once activated or triggered, an ability exists on the stack independently of its source. Destruction or removal of the source after that time won\u2019t affect the ability.  ... if the source is no longer in the zone it\u2019s expected to be in at that time, its last known information is used. The source can still perform the action even though it no longer exists.\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '21866'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2612\">holgir</span>\r\n                                (3/8/2010 1:52:31 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_c